com.camerontec.catalys.application.marketdata

Interface IInstrumentUpdateInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    InstrumentUpdateInfo

    public interface IInstrumentUpdateInfo
    Used to store information about the market data requests for an instrument and also used to store the reusable messages used for sending out data on the instrument.

      • getInstrumentDefinition

        List<ITagValue> getInstrumentDefinition()
        Returns the instrument definition in the form of a List of ITagValue.

        This returned list will always return at least one entry, being the symbol (see IInstrument.getSymbol()) as the value and Constants.TAGiSymbol (55) as the tag.

        Returns:
        List of ITagValue's defining the instrument.

      • getTopOfBookRequestedFieldIDs

        int[] getTopOfBookRequestedFieldIDs()
        Returns all requested FieldID's, grouped by their corresponding MDEntryTypes.

        Note that it is important that all FieldID's for a given MDEntryType are together in the array. The populateTopOfBookMessage method in MarketDataProcessor depends on this - otherwise field values may not appear under the correct MDEntryType entry in a FIX message.

        This is computed from the requested MDEntryTypes (as returned by getTopOfBookRequestedMDEntryTypes() when the entryTypes are first requested.

        Returns:
        FieldID's matching the requested MDEntryTypes.
